Siriboon &amp; Panha in 
<bibRefCitation author="Siriboon, T" journalOrPublisher="The Raffles Bulletin of Zoology" pageId="0" pageNumber="39" pagination="161 - 174" refId="B77" refString="Siriboon, T, Sutcharit, C, Naggs, F, Rowson, B, Panha, S, 2014b. Revision of the carnivorous snail genus Indoartemon Forcart, 1946 and a new genus Carinartemis from Thailand (Pulmonata: Streptaxidae). The Raffles Bulletin of Zoology 62: 161 - 174" title="Revision of the carnivorous snail genus Indoartemon Forcart, 1946 and a new genus Carinartemis from Thailand (Pulmonata: Streptaxidae)." volume="62" year="2014 b">Siriboon et al. 2014b</bibRefCitation>
: 166-168.
</paragraph>
